title: For many, Christmas, New Years were just two more working days
text:
Houston, MS (38851)

Today

A steady rain this morning. Showers continuing this afternoon. High 61F. Winds SW at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 100%..

Tonight

Showers early, then cloudy overnight. Low near 40F. Winds W at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 50%.
